Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp?
Curator's comments: Known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.116, 8. This piece, or either of two others drawn by Petrie, may be British Museum 2011,5003.417.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1418)
